{"tid":2293297,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"名校生向警防線擲水樽 還柙三周今判社會服務令 彭亮廷:悔意欠奉","createTime":"2020-11-20T06:52:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T08:05:25.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"7b1a1b87a915d8d574aded0644629cf4e1e1dfb4","tid":2293297,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T06:52:25.000Z","msg":"去年11月2日尖沙嘴舉行「人權民主和你Sing」活動，原獲警方發出不反對通知書，惟活動遭警方腰斬，爆發警民衝突。當晚旺角有示威者聚集，其間15歲名校男生被指向警方防線投擲膠水樽。雖然沒人被擊中，警方亦找不到水樽，但男生仍被控在公眾地方擾亂秩序，早前經審訊後裁定罪成。裁判官彭亮廷今指被告從未認罪，但考慮到被告已遭還柙三周，為取得平衡，同意判被告接受200小時社會服務令。被告父親聞判當場失聲痛哭。<br />\n<br />\n彭官再指，被告一心只為逃避拘留式刑罰，「悔意欠奉，仍要求判處社會服務令，我都係第一次見」，惟留意到被告已遭還柙21日，若判處更生中心等拘留式刑罰，必會被判拘禁數月至半年，刑罰與控罪不成正比亦不相稱，故在取得平衡下，只能判被告接受社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201120/7YBLVHBPCRE7XIMGDA2HPGO7PI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201120%2F7YBLVHBPCRE7XIMGDA2HPGO7PI%2F&d=gxBKi3yaaNwv0eARaXv6BajakGblTMbnvy6EODhsvCk%3D&h=34a93b31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201120%2F7YBLVHBPCRE7XIMGDA2HPGO7PI%2F&h=5d78ae55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201120/7YBLVHBPCRE7XIMGDA2HPGO7PI/</a>"},{"pid":"40fbffa14b6496e2e6df1d6fb5b6c6472eece6a1","tid":2293297,"uid":115910,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T06:53:01.000Z","msg":"判社會服務令個老豆喊乜撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c84bb752d3449eb4c5ab5dce8c55d0b93f3c4495","tid":2293297,"uid":76804,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T06:53:45.000Z","msg":"雖然沒人被擊中，警方亦找不到水樽<br />\n點認呀屌<br />\n擺明老屈啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69277e43a22d9da4f70f0bc94c1e9eeb4